Parents are stupid at times. THey say they trust me but it doesn't feel like it. We're good kids. A whole lot better than my brother ever was. I mean come on. They got mad at me for hangin out outside the house in the front yard. I mean geez. We are such idiots...we sat outside debating which star was the north star and what the real name was. Like alpha centari or somehting. But they were only snowed because the golden child (jeremy...who by the way still refuses to accnolage that i exist anymore) had just come and left. THey musta been mad that they were stuck with me. Why ca't they just except the fact that cassie isn't trouble and that tomm is a good driver and that we are probably the best children you could ever get. We don't drink (it would kill tomm) we don't do drugs, and we are such idiots that we sit outside watching stars (aka. planes. yes cassie couldn't tell the difference). We still hang out at the park. But thats my demented influence. go swings!

so i took one of the previous random thingys you see taking over my journal. It was about what your symbol would be and what it would mean. I got, lucifer, the devil, evil, black, darkness......hmmmm... the meaning were....control all evil, symbolic, angst, sorrow, fear, darkness, shadow, pain....hmmm..as if i couldn't take the hint. EVERY ONE WAS LIKE THAT> every name i tried that i go by. every one! brit, brittany, atalante tinwe, tweak. Every one. Scary. 

O so i was laying on the top of my car in the pitch black night next to this fog covered feild starring at the stars, thinkin howe i love my life and who i am. (even though to most people i'm not real. Just some imagined idea of who i am that doesn't exist.) And i can't wait to see what i'm gonna do with thte rest of my life. THen i got to the whole, is there life on other planets? that was funny. I like to know where i stand, and to have answers, but sometimes its the completely weird unanswerable questions that are the best. guess you'd have to know me to understand. I'm so retarted. geez. Cassie, get help fast. tomm....forget what you feel. Think with your head. as for me...i just need to stop feeling anything. Wait too late. THats what got me screwed in the first place. Damn....now i don't know anything any more.

Have you ever noticed that everybody has there own little "charm" as me and cassie have come to call it?
~Jake and robert have mastered the "Take me now" charm. 
~Mark has that "I'm everything you want until you get the chance to have it" charm. 
~Krista has that "Repell stupid people" charm. 
~Marisa has that "WHOOOO HOOOOO" charm.
~For Bri its the "Screw what you think" charm.
~April has the "Tell me all you problems" charm.
~Terri has the "Kindergarden" charm.
~Jon has the "I'm good for you as far as you know" charm. 
~Cassie's got that "Take me how i am" charm. 
~Sara has that "Loud and crazy as long as i'm not alone" charm. (Yes, the word charm isn't fiting the context anymore)
~Katie has that "pity me. My life sucks" charm. 
~Robert also has the "The world holds no joy for me, but i won't cry" thing going. 
~Nick has the "I can't die a virgin!" thing....weirdo. 
~Tomm has that "Make you laugh till you die" and "slow down the world" charm.
~Kels got the, "Can understand anything without even knowing it" charm. 
~and me? I can't tell. From what i've seen its the..."THeres something about you but eh, not intrested in YOU persay..." thing. heh. What ever anyone feels will wear off. I promise.

What is the reason for being here?

I think you have to make a reason to be here. Create a reason to live, otherwise you will let your life pass you buy as you live out some pointless existense as you tick of the days till you die. I believe you have to find something to do that fulfills your idea of 'living'. Stand up for something you believe in, do your dream job, fall in love...create a reason to be here. 

Slightly off topic but still another believe. Point of inspiration~pagans. (well i didn't make this up, its the pagan (Wiccan/celtic) motto) 

It it harms none, do what you will.
